{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762980/extras/test.gif?t=1720789701\" /><br><strong>Face Your Fear</strong> is a horror game based on a story with puzzles and a realistic and stressful atmosphere. You can\u2019t fight so you have to run, hide or look death in the eyes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">In <strong>Face Your Fear</strong>,</h2>you incarnate a young teenager attaint of a heart disease, so you will have to pay attention to your BPM and do not forget to take your medicines.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Solve the puzzles as fast as possible, but do not suffer from too much stress it would be deadly...<br><br></li><li>Alone at home while your parents are gone, you find yourself seeing paranormal events and everything seems to have changed?..<br><br></li><li>All windows are blocked and unbreakable.. The phone no longer works.. You're alone in this hell, will you fight for your survival?</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The game is currently in pre-alpha phase. If you encounter any issues or bugs, please report them to us on our Discord server. Your feedback is crucial to improving the game. Thank you very much!</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>In <strong>Face Your Fear</strong> there will be different levels, with different monsters and mechanics. Try to get out of this hell.<br><br></li><li>Immersive graphics, detailed map and stressful atmosphere.</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762980/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1720789701","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762980/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1720789701","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762980/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1720789701","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762980/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1720789701","categories":[{"des